des:
Hi! We're cousins. Carlos "Charlie", Danny, and Enrique "Kike" Montenegro. Theorists. Gamers. Musicians. Also, we love Disney, Pixar, Marvel, and Harry Potter! (Carlos is a Hufflepuff!) 

YouTube is our main platform, and here's our channel: https://bit.ly/SubToSMC . This is our videos in audio version, for on-the-go listening!

Thanks!
